content.rendered:
Directed by Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra.

Written by Hussain Dalal. Manoj Mairta. Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra.

Cast Rasika Agashe(Rabiya). Sonia Albizuri(Eva Patten). Syna Anand(Mangla). Adarsh Bharti(Ringtone). Makrand Deshpande(Sainath). Om Kanojiya(Kahnu).Atul Kulkarni. Varun Kulkarni(Bilal). Anjali Patil(Sargam). Prasad(Nirala). Nachiket Purnapatre(Sajju). Niteesh Wadhwa(Pappu). Jigyasa Yaduwanshi(Lady Cop)

Language English.

Producers P.S. Bharathi. Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra. Kanishka Mehta. Baljinder Singh. Navmeet Singh. Rajiv Tandon. Arpit Vyas.

Production Aham Brahmasmi Entertaiment. PVR Cinema. Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra Pictures.
